    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and smells just like it did the day I bought it! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and babied it since day one, so you won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like a dream and is ready to hit the road with its next lucky owner. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 43800.0,
