    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented is an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, retaining its original 2JZ-GTE power plant and Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen remains in factory configuration, featuring the sequential twin-turbocharger setup with no modifications to the wastegate or boost controller. Mechanical integrity is verified via recent compression and leak-down tests showing nominal factory tolerances across all six cylinders. The chassis is free of oxidation, with all factory VIN tags present on body panels. The interior features pristine upholstery and a crack-free dashboard. Suspension remains tight with original bushings replaced by OEM components to maintain the factory's intended damping characteristics. This is a true 'time capsule' example for the discerning collector.",
