      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior finish is breathtaking, boasting a deep, glass-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear or creasing, and the interior still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives with the precision and smoothness of the day it was first delivered. Included with the sale are both original key fobs, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, and a folder of all maintenance receipts. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example of automotive excellence for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
